<!-- Definition and uses -->
'''氟哌啶醇'''（{{lang|en|Haloperidol}}），是一種{{le|典型抗精神疾病藥物|Typical antipsychotic}}<ref name=AHFS2015/>。該藥可用於治療[[思覺失調症|思覺失調症]]、[[妥瑞氏症|妥瑞氏症]]的抽動、噁心、嘔吐、譫妄、躁動、[[思覺失調|思覺失調]]，以及[[酒精戒斷症候群|戒酒症狀]]<ref name=AHFS2015/><ref name=NEJM2014>{{cite journal|last1=Schuckit|first1=MA|title=Recognition and management of withdrawal delirium (delirium tremens).|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_new-england-journal-of-medicine_2014-11-27_371_22/page/2109|journal=The New England journal of medicine|date=27 November 2014|volume=371|issue=22|pages=2109-13|pmid=25427113}}</ref>。氟哌啶醇可透過[[口服給藥|口服]]、[[肌肉注射|肌肉注射]]、[[靜脈注射|靜脈注射]]等方法給藥<!-- <ref name=AHFS2015/> -->。藥物約會於30-60分鐘後開始作用<!-- <ref name=AHFS2015/> -->。[[思覺失調症|思覺失調症]]及相關疾病患者如果會忘記或拒絕服藥，可每四週注射一次長效配方<ref name=AHFS2015/>。

<!-- Side effects -->
氟哌啶醇有機會導致用藥人罹患[[遲發性運動障礙|遲發性運動障礙]]，可能造成永久傷害<!-- <ref name=AHFS2015/> -->。其他可能出現的副作用包含{{le|抗精神藥物惡性综合征|Neuroleptic malignant syndrome}}以及{{Le|藥源性QT間期延長症|Drug-induced QT prolongation|心臟QT間期延長}}<!-- <ref name=AHFS2015/> -->。該藥物也會提高年長[[失智症|失智症]]患者的死亡風險<ref name=AHFS2015>{{cite web|title=Haloperidol|url=http://www.drugs.com/monograph/haloperidol.html|publisher=The American Society of Health-System Pharmacists|accessdate=Jan 2, 2015|archive-date=2015-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150102120426/http://www.drugs.com/monograph/haloperidol.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[妊娠|妊娠]]期間用藥可能影響胎兒<ref name=AHFS2015/><ref name=TGA2015>{{cite web|title=Prescribing medicines in pregnancy database|url=http://www.tga.gov.au/hp/medicines-pregnancy.htm#.U1Yw8Bc3tqw|work=Australian Government|accessdate=Jan 2, 2015|date=3 March 2014|archive-date=2014-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408040902/http://www.tga.gov.au/hp/medicines-pregnancy.htm#.U1Yw8Bc3tqw|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[帕金森氏症|帕金森氏症]]患者不建議使用本藥<ref name=AHFS2015/>。

氟哌啶醇於1958年由[[保罗·杨森|保罗·杨森]]所發現<ref>{{cite book|last1=Sneader|first1=Walter|title=Drug discovery : a history|date=2005|publisher=Wiley|location=Chichester|isbn=9780471899792|page=124|edition=Rev. and updated ed.|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=Cb6BOkj9fK4C&pg=PA124|access-date=2016-03-24|archive-date=2015-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208072014/https://books.google.ca/books?id=Cb6BOkj9fK4C&pg=PA124|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是以[[哌替啶|哌替啶]]衍生而來<ref>{{cite book|last1=Ravina|first1=Enrique|title=The evolution of drug discovery : from traditional medicines to modern drugs|date=2011|publisher=Wiley-VCH|location=Weinheim|isbn=9783527326693|page=62|edition=1. Aufl.|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=iDNy0XxGqT8C&pg=PA62|access-date=2016-03-24|archive-date=2015-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208071857/https://books.google.ca/books?id=iDNy0XxGqT8C&pg=PA62|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該藥列名於[[世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单|世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单]]，為基礎醫療體系必備藥品之一<ref>{{cite web|title=WHO Model List of Essential Medicines|format=PDF|url=http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/93142/1/EML_18_eng.pdf?ua=1|work=World Health Organization|accessdate=22 April 2014|date=October 2013|pages=7, 35|archive-date=2014-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140423005004/http://apps.who.int/iris/bitstream/10665/93142/1/EML_18_eng.pdf?ua=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>，通常用作典型抗精神疾患藥物<ref name=Ste2004>{{cite book|last1=Stevens|first1=Andrew|title=Health care needs assessment : the epidemiologically based needs assessment reviews|date=2004|publisher=Radcliffe Medical|location=Abingdon|isbn=9781857758924|page=202|edition=2nd ed.|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=HCLIeMG9WgoC&pg=PA202|access-date=2016-03-24|archive-date=2015-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208072515/https://books.google.ca/books?id=HCLIeMG9WgoC&pg=PA202|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在英國，一般用藥一年的花費大約20至800[[英鎊|英鎊]]<ref>{{cite book|last1=Stein|first1=edited by George|last2=Wilkinson|first2=Greg|title=Seminars in general adult psychiatry|date=2007|publisher=Gaskell|location=London|isbn=9781904671442|page=288|edition=2. ed.|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=6PGzHFuS1xkC&pg=PA288|access-date=2016-03-24|archive-date=2015-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208073236/https://books.google.ca/books?id=6PGzHFuS1xkC&pg=PA288|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Ste2004/>。同樣劑量美國則需250美元左右<ref>{{cite book|last1=Jeste|first1=Dilip V.|title=Clinical handbook of schizophrenia|date=2011|publisher=Guilford Press|location=New York|isbn=9781609182373|page=511|edition=Pbk. ed.|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=KFMFzuL3husC&pg=PA511|access-date=2016-03-24|archive-date=2015-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208045655/https://books.google.ca/books?id=KFMFzuL3husC&pg=PA511|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

